name: Imperial Security Bureau
Text: 'Deploy on table.  Sunsdown is canceled.  ISB agents who are leaders deploy -2 to sites with ''ISB'' in title.  Once per game, may take a [Setup] Mission into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  Look Sir, Droids and your Interrupts with ''advisor'' in title may be played as follows: ''USED: Use 1 Force to take an ISB agent into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.'' (Immune to Alter.)',
